 After Obama\x{2019}s Visit (Upper left hand corner and clockwise):  1) Return [the palm] tree to the storage area.  2) Of course the exams get postponed for the guests, do you think we\x{2019}re at Harvard?  4) I saw someone practicing politics in the university sir, his name is Obama! 

 

